fern country
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:land on which bracken or <i>Paesia</i> spp. is growing or has grown; or land fit only for growing fern, or which has grown fern from earliest times


Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
